name: [ArtRaccoonee] Jenny Wakeman (XJ9)
description:
This hypernetwork can generate images in a cartoon, anime, or realistic styles. Realistic style with robot look sometimes hard to achieve! Also hyper net can produce NSFW arts.

The hypernetwork is trained on anime style model, so other models in cartoon or anime styles should be fine.

Activation tags - jenny_wakeman

For cartoon look - 2d, cartoon, cartoonlike

For more realistic/anime look - detailed, masterpiece, anime

Personally I use "Euler a" sampler and CFG scale - 7. Clip skip - 2.

Also don't forget to play with hypernet strength I prefer somewhere in the 0.6-1

On some models tag "realistic" might break stuff or generate ugly girls, so you might wanna use lower values - (realistic:0.2) or (realistic:0.4)
